==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Hurried
<hw>Hur"ried</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Urged on;
hastened; going or working at speed; <as>as, a <ex>hurried</ex> writer;
a <ex>hurried</ex> life.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Done in a hurry; hence, imperfect; careless; <as>as,
a <ex>hurried</ex> job</as>.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧A <xex>hurried</xex>
meeting.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Milton.</au></rj></p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Hur"ried*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>Hur"ried*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Hurrier</ent>⟦br⟧
